\newlabel{fig:correlations_cluster}{{5}{2}{Distribution of pairwise spike count correlations for within-cluster pairs only. The clustered network shows a heavy positive tail that increases with counting window size (50~ms vs.\ 100~ms)}{figure.caption.5}{}}
